snippet.title: Mr. Zod's Fandom Zone
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official YouTube channel for Mr. Zod’s Fandom Zone! Weekly live streams, movie/television reviews, live chats, and more!

Our Weekly Schedule:
Every Tuesday: "Tuesday Night Rant" with Zod
Every Friday (Daytime): "Tongue In Cheek with Book by J (Author, J. McCarthy)"
Every Friday Night- "Late Night Talks with co-host PB and the Bridge Crew: Purp Minded, Mad Squirrel & Cybernetic Husky."
Every Saturday Evening- "Late Night Weekends with co-host Pb and the Bridge Crew."

New shows and videos are always in development so please stay tuned!

💬 Follow on Twitter:  https://twitter.com/Generalzodfz
🎮 Twitch Channel: https://www.twitch.tv/mrzodfz 

Support Our Work:

🤝 Become a Channel Member: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVxzTQDruKuxiHvK36BSYkQ/join
